### Health check
GET http://localhost:8080/api/health

### Create an event with 5 seats
POST http://localhost:8080/api/events
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Concurrency Test Concert",
  "totalSeats": 5
}

### Fetch an event (replace {{id}})
GET http://localhost:8080/api/events/1

### Book a seat
POST http://localhost:8080/api/bookings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "eventId": 1,
  "userId": 100,
  "seatsBooked": 1
}

### List bookings for an event
GET http://localhost:8080/api/bookings/event/1

### Get a single booking
GET http://localhost:8080/api/bookings/1

### Explain a FAILED booking (replace {{id}} with a failed booking's id)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/bookings/2/explain

### Admin: verify an explanation as accurate
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/bookings/2/verify-explanation
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "accurate": true
}

### Admin: check LLM explanation accuracy rate
GET http://localhost:8080/api/admin/llm-accuracy
